N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 17 ยง 132.1 - Controller test fee

State Regulations

The fee for testing a controller for a traffic-control
signal erected pursuant to section
1681
(c) of the Vehicle and Traffic Law shall be
$271 per test. Notes
